and/or Solutions, and the development of the Platform will follow an iterative-incremental process, 
with the significant advantage that the starting point is the existing and running ORS GROUP RAMS 
4.0 platform as well as over 1,000 A.I. Algorithms and over 100 software solutions for optimizing 
value chains. The planned roadmap is represented in Figure 15 . The initial development (Phase 1) 
