the Platform. From the Phase 2, third-parties’ HSC, algorithms and solutions will be allowed to be 
hosted (upon successful certification process by ORS ), while the development of the Platform will 
proceed until its final release in Q1 of 2019 at the latest. 

The long experience at ORS GROUP in developing sophisticated software solutions, including plat-
forms, and delivering them on time to demanding international customers is the best guarantee that 
the development and business roadmap of the ORS SA Platform for Hypersmart Contracts will be 
duly and professionally executed, achieving all set goals. 

