Regulatory authorities are carefully scrutinizing businesses and operations associated to cryptocur-
rencies in the world. In that respect, regulatory measures, investigations or actions may impact ORS 
SA’s business and even limit or prevent it from developing its operations in the future. Any person 
undertaking to acquire ORST must be aware of the ORS SA business model, the white paper or terms 
